<p><b><font size=+2>What should be the advantages of the Active System
usage for this implementation?</font></b>
<hr WIDTH="100%"></center>

<ul>
<li>
<font size=+1>The computer program can make comparison and other processes
quickly.</font></li>

<li>
<font size=+1>Only the result should be shown and other redundant information
are not shown. Therefore, the result arrives quickly to the customer.</font></li>

<li>
<font size=+1>Using active system is easy more than using telephone or
other ways to make reservation.</font></li>

<li>
<font size=+1>Using graphics and controls is not necessary to enter the
input data and to show the results. This makes the usage of this program
simpler, suitable, fast and useful.</font></li>
</ul>

